title: Great people of the Bible and how they lived (History).pdf
description:
Great People of the Bible and How They Lived
Reader's Digest | 1979 | ISBN: 0895770156 | English | 440 pages | PDF | 54 MB

For those who either do not have a Biblical background, this is easy to understand and in storybook form w/out being a children's Bible. Very informative. Details added on the time period and also archeological finds. If you do have a good Biblical background, it just adds great information to an already amazing book!
